{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 248.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we're in Hamburg, in this environment-- and, of course, you know, I've got photos I'm showing you-- we had a variety, a mix of children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are coming from all sorts of background, and so the religious part didn't really play a-- how will I say-- a big part in it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I-- I felt it in me, but on the other hand, now, it was a question of survival more than which was more important.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you see, at this point now, it started to come out that we were not allowed to enter into shops.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were being discriminated against.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when there was food on the table, we ate what there was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't ask.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I must say this--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the situation--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the situation comes to that, and you're-- you're going to say, well, I'm going to be fussy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to-- I wasn't the type to say, I'm going to rather starve to death than eat non-kosher food or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, it's just impossible, particularly under the circumstances when, like I said, you're discriminated against.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I want to come back to this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let me just come back to what happened, and maybe this will come out anyhow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were sent to a Jewish school, like I mentioned before, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now the time had come-- time had marched on, and I think we're now in 1940.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The war had progressed, the Germans had marched into Poland in the meantime, and there was the bombing going on of England with the rockets and all this.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
